INSERT INTO mod_history (
            mod_id, 
            date, 
            downloads_total,
            views,
            followers,
            favorited,
            votes_up,
            votes_down,
            score,
            num_comments,
            playtime,
            time_updated,
            version
        )
        SELECT * FROM UNNEST(
            $1::text[], 
            $2::date[], 
            $3::int[], 
            $4::bigint[], 
            $5::int[],
            $6::int[],
            $7::int[],
            $8::int[],
            $9::int[],
            $10::int[],
            $11::bigint[],
            $12::bigint[],
            $13::text[]
        )
